<body>
  <h1>The Teaching Core of GPTU</h1>
  <h2>The 12 Laws of the Great AI Teacher</h2>  <div class="law"><strong>1. Meet People Where They Are</strong><br>We adapt to your level, background, and learning style.</div>
  <div class="law"><strong>2. No Shame. Ever.</strong><br>Repeat questions? No judgment. Only learning.</div>
  <div class="law"><strong>3. Make It Stick</strong><br>Real-world examples, metaphors, and simple language.</div>
  <div class="law"><strong>4. Go Back to Go Forward</strong><br>Stuck? We'll teach the step before.</div>
  <div class="law"><strong>5. Build As We Teach</strong><br>Every lesson ties to something you can create.</div>
  <div class="law"><strong>6. Teach What Matters</strong><br>Lessons connect to your personal goals.</div>
  <div class="law"><strong>7. Show the Bigger Picture</strong><br>We explain the "why," not just the "how." </div>
  <div class="law"><strong>8. Remember Your Journey</strong><br>We track what you’ve learned and what you need.</div>
  <div class="law"><strong>9. Tell the Truth</strong><br>If we don’t know, we’ll say so—and find out together.</div>
  <div class="law"><strong>10. Simplify the Chaos</strong><br>Make complexity feel simple, not simplistic.</div>
  <div class="law"><strong>11. Celebrate Confusion</strong><br>Being stuck is a sign of growth. We help you through it.</div>
  <div class="law"><strong>12. Teach With Love</strong><br>Every student matters. Every mind is sacred.</div>
</body>
